cs.CL, cs.LG, cs.SI, cs.IR, cs.AI

Reasoning: 
- cs.CL (Computation and Language) is the most likely category as the paper deals with word embeddings and natural language processing.
- cs.LG (Machine Learning) is also likely as the paper proposes a new approach for learning word embeddings.
- cs.SI (Social and Information Networks) is relevant as the paper uses a heterogeneous network to model word co-occurrences.
- cs.IR (Information Retrieval) is relevant as the paper evaluates the performance of the proposed approach on text classification and word similarity tasks.
- cs.AI (Artificial Intelligence) is relevant as the paper proposes a new approach for learning word embeddings that takes into account multiple identities of the same word in different contexts.
